<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Φλαο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ΐ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῳ Φοι</supplied>βάμμωνι <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">πο</unclear>λι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τε</unclear>υομένῳ πατρὶ π<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ό</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λεως</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Ὀξ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear>υ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear>χίτου

    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ Α<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὐρη</unclear>λίας Ἀηοῦ ἀπὸ τῆς αὐτῆς πόλεως.

    <lb n="3"/>τῶν ἀνθρωπίνων ὑπεξῆλθεν ὁ ἐμὸς ἀνὴρ <choice><corr>ἐποφείλων</corr><sic>εποφιλων</sic></choice>

    <lb n="4"/>χρέα. ὁ δὲ υἱός μου Ἀείων, γυναῖκ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><sic>ν</sic> ἑα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῷ</unclear> ἀγαγ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὼ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> καὶ

    <lb n="5"/>ἐκ τῆ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>οῦ πατρὸς αὐτοῦ ε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὐπ</unclear>ορίας <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ῶν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ραγ</supplied>μά<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ω<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear>

    <lb n="6"/>εὑρών, <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear>ελετᾷ ἐπικλᾶσα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> ἐμοὶ τῇ μ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ητ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὶ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear>έρος

    <lb n="7"/>τοῦ χρέους, ἀντιποιούμενος καὶ τοῦ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear>ο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νι</unclear>κοῦ μου

    <lb n="8"/>οἰκήματος. ὅθεν πα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>καλῶ σου τὴν

    <lb n="9"/>στερρότητα ὥστε κελεῦσαι τοῦτον πα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρα</unclear>στῆναι,

    <lb n="10"/>ἐπειδήπερ καὶ περιεποιήσατο ἑαυτῷ πράγματα,

    <lb n="11"/>ἔχοντα καὶ τοὺς νηπίους ἀδελφοὺς αὐτοῦ <choice><corr>συγκά-

    <lb n="12"/>μνοντας</corr><sic>συνκαμνοντας</sic></choice>, καὶ ἀκροάσασ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θ</unclear>αι ἡμῶν καὶ τύπον

    <lb n="13"/>δίκαιον παρασχεῖν. <milestone rend="paragraphos" unit="undefined"/> φαίνομαι γὰρ ὑπὲρ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αὐ</unclear>τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῦ</supplied> ἐν τῷ χρυσαρ-

    <lb n="14"/>γύρῳ ὑποθεμένη τὸ θυγάτριόν μου εἰς τέσσαρα <num value="4"/> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">χ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρύ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σιν</unclear>α.

    <lb n="15"/><handShift new="m2"/>Αὐρηλία Ἀηοῦ ἐπιδέδωκα.</ab></div><div n="meta.35622" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.35622" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="0498" notBefore="0465" type="textDate">465 - 498</date></p></div><div n="meta.35622" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. Feissel - Gascou, La pétition à Byzance, S. 181.</p></div><div n="meta.35622" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">63</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">4393</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">35622</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">63</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">4393</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;63;4393" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.35622" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.35622" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.35622" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH4220706a344c494ae70570"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>